<i>A Good Day to Have an Affair</i> was the feature film debut of Lee Min-ki.<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The actor that played Dew's husband, <a href="/wiki/Park_Sang-myun" title="Park Sang-myun">Park Sang-myun</a>, is the same man who played the aloof husband in <i><a href="/wiki/My_Wife_is_a_Gangster" class="mw-redirect" title="My Wife is a Gangster">My Wife is a Gangster</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/2001_in_film" title="2001 in film">2001</a>).<sup class="noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact" style="white-space:nowrap;">&#91;<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources. (August 2019)">citation needed</span></a></i>&#93;</sup>


